{"tid":730732,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"快線撚唔該入一入黎","createTime":"2018-07-05T15:42:26.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-13T06:41:20.000Z","uid":139228,"like":67,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"bd23ac0c291b85d3684973262e66896a36373e6b","tid":730732,"uid":139228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T15:42:26.000Z","msg":"屌你老味咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你地知唔知咩係快線？<br />\n快線係用黎比人爬頭用<br />\n唔撚係比你地慢慢揸架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n🐢龜速車/假日車/C9車/大貨車🚚<br />\n唔該你地鳩縮返入中線好冇？<br />\n<br />\n揸得慢，慢過限速都算<br />\n仲要同中線d車同速平排<br />\n焗後面車要慢線爬頭<br />\n(慢線同時又有慢車，屌）<br />\n真係戇鳩鳩<br />\n<br />\n揸車揸到火都黎<br />\n通常成功爬到頭都會送返隻中指比對方<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ec2e8e62dc5be04556b6065b129a08784d24af9","tid":730732,"uid":139228,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T16:53:50.000Z","msg":"邊個負評"},{"pid":"26ddfb9ed99c279a54b3a550837f56a5b8869d1d","tid":730732,"uid":129521,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T18:18:47.000Z","msg":"呠鳩佢"},{"pid":"8adc107fd7960acdcf989f4d5e8601c02de20fde","tid":730732,"uid":42314,"like":3,"dislike":14,"score":-11,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T18:19:58.000Z","msg":"洗唔洗咁燥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aee8f2b94d0c5b0fcdfdcea08472ba5b95ad987b","tid":730732,"uid":3548,"like":9,"dislike":4,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"8adc107fd7960acdcf989f4d5e8601c02de20fde","tid":730732,"uid":42314,"like":3,"dislike":14,"score":-11,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T18:19:58.000Z","msg":"洗唔洗咁燥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgm